         <abstract id="aspace_36e163ebe17223c2e723ddf943ab2e36">The records consist of minutes, reports, memoranda, rosters, agendas, and reviews documenting the activities of the Council on Planning and Priorities and the Executive Committee of the Yale Faculty of Arts and Sciences.</abstract>
